MATCH (a2)<--(a1)<--(a0)<--(b)-->(c0)-->(c1)-->(c2)-->(c3)-->(c4)
WHERE a2.VALUE='PREVIEWS' AND a2.PATH='/HTML/BODY/DIV/DIV/DIV/DIV/DIV/DIV/DIV/DIV/DIV/DIV/SPAN/text()' AND a2.POSITION='1' 
AND a1.VALUE='SPAN' AND a1.POSITION='1' 
AND a0.VALUE='DIV' AND a0.POSITION='3' 
AND b.VALUE='DIV' 
AND c0.VALUE='DIV' AND c0.POSITION='6' 
AND c1.VALUE='DIV' AND c1.POSITION='23' 
AND c2.VALUE='DIV' AND c2.POSITION='2' 
AND c3.VALUE='I' AND c3.POSITION='1' 
AND c4.NODE_TYPE='3' AND c4.POSITION='1' 
 RETURN c4.VALUE AS VALUE, c4.URL AS URL, 'Template' in LABELS(c4) as template
